value.0: Ansgar is a tall and strong man, swinging his axe with quick, precise movements.

This set of clothing has been made to be highly resistant to the cold. The insides are fur lined and the leather has been treated with enchantments. No sign of the maker remains and so it stays a mystery as to how it ended up in the dark lair it was once found in.
Jorun is one of the villages young women, clearly accustomed to her surroundings demanding weather.
A dressy tunic with fancy undershirt and shoes.
From time to time, highwaymen are forced against preference to fight pitched battles. The more well-heeled of such individuals oftimes wear these chainshirts when expecting such instances.
This portly man is the villages local priest - and near continuously inebriated.

This tinderbox allows you to create a campfire to warm your bones after a hard day's fighting.  One should use caution and restraint with such an item, as it may draw the attentions of unwanted visitors...

A guige is a long strap, typically made of leather, used to hang a shield on the shoulder or neck when not in use. Used in combat, it freed a soldier to use a weapon requiring two hands (or a weapon in each hand) without discarding the shield; the shield could then be easily retrieved when needed.
